  "description": "<i>Die Alien Slime</i> is a simple shooter with top-down perspective, like <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Alien+Syndrome\">Alien Syndrome</a>. The player controls a lone spaceman, who must fight against aliens and activate special terminals. Many of these terminals can be found scattered around the ship. In the space base there are many barriers: doors, transport blocks and energy barriers. The space base is a labyrinth, colonized by hundreds of aliens. ",
